## Metrics Table Format

```markdown
## Schema Documentation Progress

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Schema** | {Schema} |
| **Total Objects** | {total} |
| **Tables** | {table_count} |
| **Views** | {view_count} |
| **Documented** | {documented} ({pct}%) |
| **Failed** | {failed} |
| **Skipped** | {skipped} |
| **Last Updated** | {date} |
```
